{"title_page": "Nabapally Boys' High School", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2015}}\n{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}\n{{Infobox school\n|name                   = Nabapally Boys' High School\n|native_name            = \n|latin_name             = \n|logo                   = \n|seal_image             = \n|image                  = \n|image_size             = \n|alt                    = \n|caption                = \n|motto                  = \n|motto_translation      = \n|location               =\n|streetaddress          = Boys school Road\n|region                 = [[Barasat]], [[North 24 Parganas]]\n|city                   = \n|state                  = [[West Bengal]]\n|province               = \n|county                 = [[India]]\n|postcode               = \n|postalcode             = \n|zipcode                = 700126\n|country                = India\n|country1               = \n|coordinates            = {{coord|22|43|11.3|N|88|28|8.1|E|type:edu_region:IN|display=inline,title}}\n|schooltype             = Government school\n|fundingtype            = \n|type                   = \n|religious_affiliation  = \n|religion               = \n|denomination           = \n|patron                 = \n|established            = 1963<!-- {{Start date|df=yes|1963|01|}} -->\n|founded                = \n|opened                 = \n|founder                = \n|status                 = \n|closed                 =\n|locale                 = \n|sister_school          = \n|schoolboard            = \n|district               = \n|us_nces_district_id    = \n|LEA                    = \n|authority              = \n|category               = \n|category_label         = \n|oversight              = \n|oversight_label        = \n|authorizer             = \n|superintendent         = \n|trustee                = \n|specialist             = \n|session                = \n|schoolnumber           = \n|school code            = \n|MOE                    = \n|of